</head>
<body>



	<!-- Primary Page Layout
	================================================== -->

	<!-- Delete everything in this .container and get started on your own site! -->

	<%= render "layouts/userbar" %>

	<div class="container body">
		<a href="index.html"><h1 class="logo">Nice Neighbor</h1></a>
		<div class="one-third column callToAction">
			<h2>Sign Up!</h2>
			<p class="tag">Become part of a network of helpful neighbors.
			<span>Help a neighbor out</span></p>
		</div>
		<div class="two-thirds column signUp">
			 <form id="mailinglistform" method="post" action="/mailinglist/subscribe/">
				<div style="display:none"><input type="hidden" value="ca916f18bbf5851357e155350311455d" name="csrfmiddlewaretoken"></div>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<label for="id_email">Email</label>
						<input type="email" placeholder="enter your email address" id="id_email" name="email" class="transparent">
					</li>
					<li>
						<label for="id_zip">Phone Number</label>
						<input type="phone" maxlength="12" pattern="[0-9]{5}" placeholder="phone number e.g. 503-123-4567" id="id_phone" name="phone" class="transparent">
					</li>
					<li>
						<label for="id_zip">Zip code</label>
						<input type="zip" maxlength="5" pattern="[0-9]{5}" placeholder="and zip code" id="id_zipcode" name="zipcode" class="transparent">
					</li>
					<li>
					    <button type="submit" id="joinBtn">
					        <span>Join</span>
					    </button>
				    </li>
				</ul>
				<div class="clear"></div>
			</form>
		</div>
		<div class="one-third column">
			<div class="clear"></div>
			<h3>How it Works</h3>
			<img width="300" height="187" alt="Cells" src="/images/cells.png">
			<ol>
			<li>Sign up ! All you need is your name, email address and phone number.</li>
			<li>Submit a request for the item / items you need in your city.</li>
			<li>You can also respond to requests from your neighbors by searching in your area.</li>
			<li>Overall, NiceNeighbor allows you to connect with your fellow neighbors and lend a helping hand.</li>
		</ol>
		</div>
		<div class="two-thirds column quotes">
			<h3>What Your Neighbors are saying</h3>
			<blockquote>NiceNeighbor is revolutionizing the way neighbors interact</blockquote>
			<blockquote>Easy to use and effective: would recommend NiceNeighbor to all my friends</blockquote>
			<blockquote>So helpful and convenient, connected the whole neighborhood</blockquote>
			<h3>Case in Point</h3>
			<div class="five columns">
				<img width="140" height="144" alt="Lady" src="/images/lady.png">
			</div>
			<div class="five columns">
				<img width="140" height="192" alt="Gent" src="/images/gent.png">
			</div>
			<div class="five columns panelOne">
				<h4>Frantic Request from Sue:</h4>
				<p>I need a saw !, a tree has fallen on my house during this hurricane, and my son is trapped. <em>PLEASE HELP</em></p>
			</div>
			<div class="five columns panelTwo">
				<h4>Urgent Response from Fred</h4>
				<p>Sue, I will be right over, I have a saw and I am certified lumberjack. We will free your son.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="ten columns panelThree">
				<h4>Sue's son survived the horrible hurricane due to kinda help and assistance from NiceNeighbor </h4>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div><!-- container -->
	<div class="container footer">
		<p>This project is one of many entries in the <a href="http://www.sunlightfoundation.com">Sunlight Foundation's</a> Labs Olympics competition. It doesn't actually exist, and our quotes and stories are entirely made up. You may be fooled by the fact that it's super duper awesome...and actually works, but don't let us trick you.</p>
	</div>


	<!-- JS
	================================================== -->
	<script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/javascripts/tabs.js"></script>

<!-- End Document
================================================== -->

</body></html>